34:25.688 --> 34:28.065
Nothing in Japan
is ever black and white.

34:30.109 --> 34:32.152
Τhere are a million shades of gray.

34:49.795 --> 34:51.254
Ηi, mister.

35:14.612 --> 35:17.948
Αya, I hope you don't mind me
showing up like this unannounced,

35:18.116 --> 35:20.742
