in the Philippines,

35:20.910 --> 35:22.744
and I got an assignment
to come to Japan.

35:22.912 --> 35:24.621
Since I was nowhere near
the neighborhood, I thought...

35:24.789 --> 35:26.206
Please, go away.

35:28.751 --> 35:32.420
