35:32.588 --> 35:34.089
none of which you returned.

35:34.257 --> 35:35.674
You shouldn't have come.

35:49.939 --> 35:51.815
Good morning.

36:13.004 --> 36:14.379
Shimada Sensei...

36:31.272 --> 36:33.064
Τhey are going to call the police.

36:34.150 --> 36:35.775
May I walk with you a little bit?

36:49.957 --> 36:53.376
My father made me promise
one thing,

36:53.544 --> 36:56.254
