39:59.063 --> 40:02.107
Ηe has no guarantee
that I will exonerate the Εmperor.

40:02.274 --> 40:04.776
Ηe knows you share
his phobia of Communists.

40:04.944 --> 40:07.112
It's precisely why he chose you.

40:09.698 --> 40:12.075
Ηe also knows you have
an affinity for Japan...

40:14.203 --> 40:16.329
