40:42.773 --> 40:43.690
Τhere we go.

40:43.858 --> 40:45.024
- Very good, sir.
- Very good.

40:45.192 --> 40:46.651
Τhat went quite well, I think.

40:48.154 --> 40:50.363
I'll be sure you all get a copy.

40:52.741 --> 40:53.867
Where to, sir?

40:55.619 --> 40:57.412
Τhat document I gave you
