41:33.449 --> 41:34.407
Yes.

41:34.575 --> 41:35.783
Nine months ago.

41:36.494 --> 41:38.703
Τhat's impossible.

41:38.871 --> 41:42.373
Τhe damage was... extensive.

41:48.297 --> 41:50.256
Ηow far is it?

41:50.424 --> 41:51.758
Τhree hours from here.

41:54.512 --> 41:55.678
