56:51.282 --> 56:52.324
Tell him!

57:26.651 --> 57:28.235
MacArthur.

57:59.893 --> 58:02.561
Just you. No weapons.

58:09.319 --> 58:10.360
Wait here.

58:10.528 --> 58:11.695
Yes, sir.

58:43.686 --> 58:45.979
