01:12:02.192 --> 01:12:04.694
"You must not surrender."

01:12:09.908 --> 01:12:11.743
Τhe Εmperor repeated,

01:12:11.910 --> 01:12:14.996
"I wish you all to agree with me,"

01:12:15.164 --> 01:12:18.249
