01:14:10.362 --> 01:14:13.614
At 8:00 a.m.,
General Tanaka arrived

01:14:13.782 --> 01:14:15.783
and stopped the soldiers,

01:14:15.951 --> 01:14:19.287
and many of the officers
shot themselves.

01:14:19.455 --> 01:14:23.624
Τhen General Tanaka
went into his room

01:14:23.792 --> 01:14:25.501
