the way you just told me.

01:14:53.489 --> 01:14:55.698
All records were destroyed,

01:14:56.992 --> 01:14:59.702
and many witnesses
killed themselves.

01:15:01.371 --> 01:15:04.373
You can believe me or not,

01:15:04.541 --> 01:15:09.378
