01:23:09.067 --> 01:23:13.320
In the end, I am where I belong,

01:23:13.488 --> 01:23:16.991
but my heart is with you always.

01:23:19.494 --> 01:23:22.663
Yours, Aya.

01:24:51.252 --> 01:24:53.754
